12px] text-neutral-600\">Storm Gray</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/5/156EDEC31CC30D4A63BBF05BCDAE6489.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bm</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Brown Mahogany</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/C/AC554AED01408F12A4CA4216F04E8855.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bs</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black Stain</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">wl</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">White Lacquer</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Add 15% to product price for a white lacquer finish.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/E/4/E4BDC3C73C851BC3A163B3A2764E27C1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">bl</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black Lacquer</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Add 15% to product price for a black lacquer finish.</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Clip Finish</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/9/6/9635A17C6CBACBAAFBAAD7837D4074E5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Clip - Brass</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/A/2/A2D180ED77806DA761CFE003FEBB6FAA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Clip - Antique Brass</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/7/479A57E5003D87871E9220B1A02D68AF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Clip - Silver</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/4/3/43A713B45673D4B7FCF9B730B1357AC6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Clip - Black</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Laser Engraving (add'l location or size)</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">The listed product price includes a one position laser engraving up to the size stated (If it shows no setup, the price does not include decoration.)  Additional positions and/or sizes may be added for the prices shown.\r\n\r\nLaser Set up policy:\texact repeat within 6 mo N/C; within 1-2 years 50%</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Laser Engrave Run</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Laser Engrave Run Charge</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">$2.00 (G) up to 4 sq. in.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Laser Engrave Charge +size</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Laser Engrave Run Charge +size</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">$.40 (G) per square inch after 4 sq. in.</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Less Than Minimum</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">The minimum quantity of any standard inventory item is limited to one half of the first quantity listed for that item on our website or catalog. Please use the first quantity price as listed in the catalog and add $ 35.00 (G) for blank merchandise and $ 70.00 (G) for decorated merchandise. Setup discounts on repeat orders do not apply to less than minimum purchases.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">LTM-B</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Blank Less Than Minimum</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$35.00 per order</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">LTM-D</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Decorated Less Than Minimum</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$70.00 per order</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Proofs</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Proofs are available on request.  To see your artwork at the actual size and location as it will appear on your finished order, request a paper or digital proof. First digital proof is free with all orders; all additional proofs are $ 7.00.\r\nTo see the actual product with your artwork on it as it will be completed, request a sample proof ($ 60.00 per product plus cost of the item - 7 WD or less after receipt of artwork approval); unless the product has a die cast component, then it is $ 95.00 plus product cost and 12 working days after artwork approval.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Paper</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Paper Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">One proof is provided with each order free of charge.  There is a charge for any subsequent proofs or changes.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$7.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Sample</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Sample Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">An actual piece as you have ordered.  7 working days after receipt of order and artwork approval.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$70.00 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">Sample, dc</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Sample Proof, die cast</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">An actual piece, die casted as you have ordered.  12 working days after receipt of order and artwork approval.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$95.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Check Presenter with Clip. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">1348-clip</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>7 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">12</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}